com.krobothsoftware.commons.parse

Class ParserJson

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.krobothsoftware.commons.parse.ParserJson
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParserInitializable

    public final class ParserJson
extends Object
implements ParserInitializable
    Json Parser part of SNC-EXT-JSON which parses HandlerJson handlers. The Json library used to parse is Jackson JSON Parse. Not to be confused with the class name JsonParser.
    Since:
    SNC-EXT-JSON 1.0
